lead_paragraph: Barcelona coach Luis Enrique expects his team to adapt to Lionel Messi's absence in the same manner as last season when they won eight of their 10 games without the talismanic forward.

headline.print_headline: Barca Must Adapt to Messi's Absence, Says Luis Enrique
